# Componentes Astro

## Estructura del frontmatter

```astro
---
// 1. Imports (layouts, componentes, lib)
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { getPublishedPosts } from '@/lib/collections';

// 2. Types
type Props = { title: string; date: Date };

// 3. Props destructuring
const { title, date } = Astro.props;

// 4. Data fetching / lógica
const posts = await getPublishedPosts();
---
```

## Tailwind CSS v4

- Usar nombres canónicos: `shrink-0` (no `flex-shrink-0`), `bg-linear-to-br` (no `bg-gradient-to-br`), `grow` (no `flex-grow`)
- Usar variables custom del tema: `text-via-green`, `bg-via-bg-content`, etc.
- NO usar `@apply` nunca
- Clases responsive: mobile-first (`md:`, `lg:`)

## Enlaces

- Links internos: rutas relativas (`/nosotros/`, `/posts/slug/`)
- Links externos: siempre `target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"`
- Aplicar `no-underline` en nav/botones, `underline` en prosa

## Imports con alias

- `@/` → `src/`
- `@components/` → `src/components/`
- `@layouts/` → `src/layouts/`
